CHECK:COMPARISON_TO_NULL: Comparison to NULL could be written "portp"
#82: FILE: drivers/char/istallion.c:773:
+		if (portp != NULL) {

Comparisons to NULL in the form (foo == NULL) or (foo != NULL)
are better written as (!foo) and (foo).

