ERROR:ASSIGN_IN_IF: do not use assignment in if condition
#167: FILE: drivers/char/istallion.c:4046:
+	if ((brdp->brdnr = stli_getbrdnr()) < 0) { /* TODO: locking */

Do not use assignments in if condition.
Example::

  if ((foo = bar(...)) < BAZ) {

should be written as::

  foo = bar(...);
  if (foo < BAZ) {

